title: (Mon Early Bird) What’s the Haps: Eddie’s Wife Is In Love with a Country Artist + Cole Swindell on Online Scammers + Bobby Feud: Favorite Disney Movies

description:
We all share our What’s the Haps from over the weekend that include Amy’s card getting declined at dinner and the country artist that Eddie’s wife is in love with. We did a round of Bobby Feud where we tried to name America’s Top Favorite 10 Disney movies.
